  "method": [
    "To prepare the dressing, mix lime juice, cumin, honey, salt, and",
    "garlic.",
    "Gradually pour the oils while stirring it continuously.",
    "Season to taste and put more pepper and salt, if required. Then set it",
    "aside.",
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees F to get it ready for preparing tortilla",
    "strips.",
    "Put tortillas on the cutting board, and cut them half.",
    "Transfer the tortilla strips to a pan, then drizzle them with oil.",
    "Add salt, then bake for around 15-20 minutes, while stirring it",
    "continuously until it is golden brown. Set aside.",
    "To prepare the salad, put corn in the oven, the cook for almost 3",
    "minutes.",
    "Cut out the bottom of the corn, then pull back silks and husks and",
    "silks.",
    "Cut corn kernels from the husks. Set them aside.",
    "Mix other ingredients and corn in a bowl. Mix to combine.",
    "Pour dressing and stir well.",
    "Add cilantro leaves for garnishing.",
    "Serve with the tortilla strips on the top."
